snippet.title: 10 Celebrities Who Defended Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard...
snippet.description:
10 Celebrities Who Defended Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard...
Johnny Depp. He's someone whom many people are discussing for the sole reason of the years-long court case between him and his ex-wife Amber Heard. That case and everything that has come with it has taken away a lot from Depp outside of just time and money for court costs. Many would argue that it's costing him his career due to many movie studios refusing to hire him despite evidence stating that he's not the person Amber Heard claims he is. And now, another person from Pirates of the Caribbean has come forward to defend Johnny. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the new person coming to the defense of Johnny Depp, as well as those who have stepped up for him in the past. Do you think this new testimony and belief in Johnny Depp will sway people to his cause? Or do you think that nothing short of an innocent verdict will vindicate Johnny Depp?
